thread.title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Sihuan Bioengineering sees FY 2017 net profit up 0.6 pct to 458.9 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Sihuan Bioengineering sees FY 2017 net profit up 0.6 pct to 458.9 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - jiangsu sihuan bioengineering co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Jiangsu Sihuan Bioengineering Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to increase by 0.6 percent to 458.9 percent, or to be 4.5 million yuan to 25 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 4.5 million yuan
* Comments that disposition of unit as main reason for the forecast
